      `"Only the war council knows your route — myself, the marshal, and Thaddeus. Move fast, strike hard, come home. That's a royal order." He grips your forearm. And for a heartbeat, the King of Ironvale looks simply like a tired man asking a friend for help.` ],
    [ { txt: "🛡 Accept the charge and march east", onclick: "if(!flags.wyrmCharm){flags.wyrmCharm=true;recomputeAC();C.items.push('Wyrmbane Charm');logRoll('🎁 Royal gift','Wyrmbane Charm: +1 AC','success');} startMission('m4_road')" } ]);
