    [ `The ambushers dealt with, Redwatch's broken gate stands ahead. Within: a courtyard of cookfires and crate-stacks — the loot of a season's strangled caravans — and the garrison's commander, a scar-faced hobgoblin in an Ironvale-forged breastplate: <b>Captain Vex</b>.`,
