      `"They wouldn't even tell me which yard," Anna says. Her hands are perfectly still. It's the stillness of someone who has decided not to shatter. "You find people. Find mine."`,
      `<i>Sera's note in the margin: yard three, by the tannery sluice. Convoy leaves within days.</i>` ],
    [ { txt: "📜 Walk in with forged release papers", req: `(Investigation, DC 13${flags.opsDone && flags.opsDone.includes("B") ? ", advantage — you own the King's own typeface" : ""}) <span class="win">✓ Tessa walks out the front gate (+4 Hearts)</span> · <span class="lose">✗ the forgery is questioned — whistles, and it gets loud</span>`, onclick: "folkTessaPapers()" },
