    <p style="max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 18px;font-size:.92em">D&amp;D-style rules: d20 checks, advantage, leveling, shops &amp; training — and backstories that <b>unlock unique paths</b> through a two-campaign, twelve-chapter saga with branching endings — the first chapters of the nation's continuing story.</p>
    <div class="action-row">
      ${(() => { const m = autosaveMeta(); return m ? `<button class="primary" style="font-size:1.15em;padding:14px 30px" onclick="loadSaveCode(Store.get(AUTOSAVE_KEY))">▶ Continue — ${esc(m.name)}, Lv ${m.level} ${esc(m.cls)} (${CHAPTER_NAMES[m.chapter] || "Ch. " + m.chapter})</button>` : ""; })()}
      <button ${autosaveMeta() ? "" : 'class="primary" style="font-size:1.15em;padding:14px 30px"'} onclick="renderCreation()">⚔ Forge Your Hero</button>
